{"thag18.1:0.1":"Theragatha 18.1 ","thag18.1:0.2":"Cattalisanipata ","thag18.1:0.3":"Pathamavagga ","thag18.1:0.4":"Mahakassapattheragatha ","thag18.1:1.1":"“Na ganena purakkhato care, ","thag18.1:1.2":"Vimano hoti samadhi dullabho; ","thag18.1:1.3":"Nanajanasangaho dukho, ","thag18.1:1.4":"Iti disvana ganam na rocaye. ","thag18.1:2.1":"Na kulani upabbaje muni, ","thag18.1:2.2":"Vimano hoti samadhi dullabho; ","thag18.1:2.3":"So ussukko rasanugiddho, ","thag18.1:2.4":"Attham rincati yo sukhavaho. ","thag18.1:3.1":"Pankoti hi nam avedayum, ","thag18.1:3.2":"Yayam vandanapujana kulesu; ","thag18.1:3.3":"Sukhumam sallam durubbaham, ","thag18.1:3.4":"Sakkaro kapurisena dujjaho. ","thag18.1:4.1":"Senasanamha oruyha, ","thag18.1:4.2":"nagaram pindaya pavisim; ","thag18.1:4.3":"Bhunjantam purisam kutthim, ","thag18.1:4.4":"sakkaccam tam upatthahim. ","thag18.1:5.1":"So me pakkena hatthena, ","thag18.1:5.2":"alopam upanamayi; ","thag18.1:5.3":"Alopam pakkhipantassa, ","thag18.1:5.4":"anguli cettha chijjatha. ","thag18.1:6.1":"Kuttamulanca nissaya, ","thag18.1:6.2":"alopam tam abhunjisam; ","thag18.1:6.3":"Bhunjamane va bhutte va, ","thag18.1:6.4":"jeguccham me na vijjati. ","thag18.1:7.1":"Uttitthapindo aharo, ","thag18.1:7.2":"putimuttanca osadham; ","thag18.1:7.3":"Senasanam rukkhamulam, ","thag18.1:7.4":"pamsukulanca civaram; ","thag18.1:7.5":"Yassete abhisambhutva, ","thag18.1:7.6":"sa ve catuddiso naro. ","thag18.1:8.1":"Yattha eke vihannanti, ","thag18.1:8.2":"aruhanta siluccayam; ","thag18.1:8.3":"Tassa buddhassa dayado, ","thag18.1:8.4":"sampajano patissato; ","thag18.1:8.5":"Iddhibalenupatthaddho, ","thag18.1:8.6":"kassapo abhiruhati. ","thag18.1:9.1":"Pindapatapatikkanto, ","thag18.1:9.2":"selamaruyha kassapo; ","thag18.1:9.3":"Jhayati anupadano, ","thag18.1:9.4":"pahinabhayabheravo. ","thag18.1:10.1":"Pindapatapatikkanto, ","thag18.1:10.2":"selamaruyha kassapo; ","thag18.1:10.3":"Jhayati anupadano, ","thag18.1:10.4":"dayhamanesu nibbuto. ","thag18.1:11.1":"Pindapatapatikkanto, ","thag18.1:11.2":"selamaruyha kassapo; ","thag18.1:11.3":"Jhayati anupadano, ","thag18.1:11.4":"katakicco anasavo. ","thag18.1:12.1":"Karerimalavitata, ","thag18.1:12.2":"bhumibhaga manorama; ","thag18.1:12.3":"Kunjarabhiruda ramma, ","thag18.1:12.4":"te sela ramayanti mam. ","thag18.1:13.1":"Nilabbhavanna rucira, ","thag18.1:13.2":"varisita sucindhara; ","thag18.1:13.3":"Indagopakasanchanna, ","thag18.1:13.4":"te sela ramayanti mam. ","thag18.1:14.1":"Nilabbhakutasadisa, ","thag18.1:14.2":"kutagaravarupama; ","thag18.1:14.3":"Varanabhiruda ramma, ","thag18.1:14.4":"te sela ramayanti mam. ","thag18.1:15.1":"Abhivuttha rammatala, ","thag18.1:15.2":"naga isibhi sevita; ","thag18.1:15.3":"Abbhunnadita sikhihi, ","thag18.1:15.4":"te sela ramayanti mam. ","thag18.1:16.1":"Alam jhayitukamassa, ","thag18.1:16.2":"pahitattassa me sato; ","thag18.1:16.3":"Alam me atthakamassa, ","thag18.1:16.4":"pahitattassa bhikkhuno. ","thag18.1:17.1":"Alam me phasukamassa, ","thag18.1:17.2":"pahitattassa bhikkhuno; ","thag18.1:17.3":"Alam me yogakamassa, ","thag18.1:17.4":"pahitattassa tadino. ","thag18.1:18.1":"Umapupphena samana, ","thag18.1:18.2":"gaganavabbhachadita; ","thag18.1:18.3":"Nanadijaganakinna, ","thag18.1:18.4":"te sela ramayanti mam. ","thag18.1:19.1":"Anakinna gahatthehi, ","thag18.1:19.2":"migasanghanisevita; ","thag18.1:19.3":"Nanadijaganakinna, ","thag18.1:19.4":"te sela ramayanti mam. ","thag18.1:20.1":"Acchodika puthusila, ","thag18.1:20.2":"gonangulamigayuta; ","thag18.1:20.3":"Ambusevalasanchanna, ","thag18.1:20.4":"te sela ramayanti mam. ","thag18.1:21.1":"Na pancangikena turiyena, ","thag18.1:21.2":"Rati me hoti tadisi; ","thag18.1:21.3":"Yatha ekaggacittassa, ","thag18.1:21.4":"Samma dhammam vipassato. ","thag18.1:22.1":"Kammam bahukam na karaye, ","thag18.1:22.2":"Parivajjeyya janam na uyyame; ","thag18.1:22.3":"Ussukko so rasanugiddho, ","thag18.1:22.4":"Attham rincati yo sukhavaho. ","thag18.1:23.1":"Kammam bahukam na karaye, ","thag18.1:23.2":"Parivajjeyya anattaneyyametam; ","thag18.1:23.3":"Kicchati kayo kilamati, ","thag18.1:23.4":"Dukkhito so samatham na vindati. ","thag18.1:24.1":"Otthappahatamattena, ","thag18.1:24.2":"attanampi na passati; ","thag18.1:24.3":"Patthaddhagivo carati, ","thag18.1:24.4":"aham seyyoti mannati. ","thag18.1:25.1":"Aseyyo seyyasamanam, ","thag18.1:25.2":"balo mannati attanam; ","thag18.1:25.3":"Na tam vinnu pasamsanti, ","thag18.1:25.4":"patthaddhamanasam naram. ","thag18.1:26.1":"Yo ca seyyohamasmiti, ","thag18.1:26.2":"naham seyyoti va pana; ","thag18.1:26.3":"Hino tamsadiso vati, ","thag18.1:26.4":"vidhasu na vikampati. ","thag18.1:27.1":"Pannavantam tatha tadim, ","thag18.1:27.2":"silesu susamahitam; ","thag18.1:27.3":"Cetosamathamanuttam, ","thag18.1:27.4":"tance vinnu pasamsare. ","thag18.1:28.1":"Yassa sabrahmacarisu, ","thag18.1:28.2":"garavo nupalabbhati; ","thag18.1:28.3":"Araka hoti saddhamma, ","thag18.1:28.4":"nabhato puthavi yatha. ","thag18.1:29.1":"Yesanca hiriottappam, ","thag18.1:29.2":"sada samma upatthitam; ","thag18.1:29.3":"Virulhabrahmacariya te, ","thag18.1:29.4":"tesam khina punabbhava. ","thag18.1:30.1":"Uddhato capalo bhikkhu, ","thag18.1:30.2":"pamsukulena paruto; ","thag18.1:30.3":"Kapiva sihacammena, ","thag18.1:30.4":"na so tenupasobhati. ","thag18.1:31.1":"Anuddhato acapalo, ","thag18.1:31.2":"nipako samvutindriyo; ","thag18.1:31.3":"Sobhati pamsukulena, ","thag18.1:31.4":"sihova girigabbhare. ","thag18.1:32.1":"Ete sambahula deva, ","thag18.1:32.2":"iddhimanto yasassino; ","thag18.1:32.3":"Dasadevasahassani, ","thag18.1:32.4":"sabbe te brahmakayika. ","thag18.1:33.1":"Dhammasenapatim viram, ","thag18.1:33.2":"mahajhayim samahitam; ","thag18.1:33.3":"Sariputtam namassanta, ","thag18.1:33.4":"titthanti panjalikata. ","thag18.1:34.1":"‘Namo te purisajanna, ","thag18.1:34.2":"namo te purisuttama; ","thag18.1:34.3":"Yassa te nabhijanama, ","thag18.1:34.4":"yampi nissaya jhayati. ","thag18.1:35.1":"Accheram vata buddhanam, ","thag18.1:35.2":"gambhiro gocaro sako; ","thag18.1:35.3":"Ye mayam nabhijanama, ","thag18.1:35.4":"valavedhisamagata’. ","thag18.1:36.1":"Tam tatha devakayehi, ","thag18.1:36.2":"pujitam pujanaraham; ","thag18.1:36.3":"Sariputtam tada disva, ","thag18.1:36.4":"kappinassa sitam ahu. ","thag18.1:37.1":"Yavata buddhakhettamhi, ","thag18.1:37.2":"thapayitva mahamunim; ","thag18.1:37.3":"Dhutagune visitthoham, ","thag18.1:37.4":"sadiso me na vijjati. ","thag18.1:38.1":"Paricinno maya sattha, ","thag18.1:38.2":"katam buddhassa sasanam; ","thag18.1:38.3":"Ohito garuko bharo, ","thag18.1:38.4":"natthi dani punabbhavo. ","thag18.1:39.1":"Na civare na sayane, ","thag18.1:39.2":"bhojane nupalimpati; ","thag18.1:39.3":"Gotamo anappameyyo, ","thag18.1:39.4":"mulalapuppham vimalamva; ","thag18.1:39.5":"Ambuna nekkhammaninno, ","thag18.1:39.6":"tibhavabhinissato. ","thag18.1:40.1":"Satipatthanagivo so, ","thag18.1:40.2":"saddhahattho mahamuni; ","thag18.1:40.3":"Pannasiso mahanani, ","thag18.1:40.4":"sada carati nibbuto”ti. ","thag18.1:40.5":"… Mahakassapo thero … ","thag18.1:40.6":"Cattalisanipato nitthito. ","thag18.1:41.0":"Tatruddanam ","thag18.1:41.1":"Cattalisanipatamhi, ","thag18.1:41.2":"mahakassapasavhayo; ","thag18.1:41.3":"Ekova thero gathayo, ","thag18.1:41.4":"cattalisa duvepi cati. "}